<!-- 
Are you unsettled by how often your phone seems to know what you're thinking?
Ever see a TV show clip just after watching it on your TV?

We were too. Well, maybe you're not *that* paranoid, but you've probably noticed the oddities.

Covered by Cordier was built for those who care about reclaiming control — over their space, over their conversations, and over their peace of mind. Our cases come with physical sliders that cover all front and rear-facing cameras, microphones, and LIDAR sensors.

This site collects only essential data for performance. Nothing more. No trackers, no 3rd-party snooping. It's individually owned and operated — the way privacy should be.
